friendlyName.description: Name that is displayed in the visual editor.

helperText.description: Tool-tip text that is displayed next to the input field in the CMS.

hideFromUI.description: Don't display in the option tab.

name.description: Name of attribute that will be passed in props to the component.

regex.description: Regex field validation for all string types (text, longText, html, url, etc)

message.description:
Friendly message to display to end-users if the regex fails, e.g.
"You must use a relative url starting with '/...' "

options.description: flags for the RegExp constructor, e.g. "gi"
